Package unidue.ub.statistics.stock

Analysis and evaluation of stock related properties.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DapBuilder
    Offers methods for building and managing of date-and-price lists.
    DAPList2JSONArray
    Transforming the date-and-price lists to JSON array.
    DateAndPrice
    Plain old java object holding the combination of date and price.
    GHBPersistence
    Persisting the xml files for the Gesamthochschulsystematik.
    StockAnalysisAssistantServlet
    Retrieves and displays the analysis of a set of documents as defined by a StockControlProperties with respect to usage properties.
    StockAnalyzerServlet
    Prepares analysis with respect to time, counter, price and collection.
    StockEvolution
    Plain old java object holding the time, counter, collection, price and notation.
    StockEvolutionManipulator
    Methods to build and manipulate stock evolution lists.
    StockUsageAnalysisServlet
    Servlet class to retrieve and prepare DocumentAnalysis for display.
